WEBVTT

1
00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:35.000
<c.transcription>［ワキ］是は都北山紫野</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] I am a priest living at Urin-in in Murasakino,)</c>

2
00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:48.000
<c.transcription>雲林院に住居する僧にて候。</c>
<c.translation>(in the Northern hills of the capital.)</c>

3
00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:59.000
<c.transcription>さても我一夏の間花を立て候。</c>
<c.translation>(I have offered flowers throughout the summer.)</c>

4
00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:10.000
<c.transcription>早安居も過方になり候へば</c>
<c.translation>(As my period of retreat is coming to a close,)</c>

5
00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:18.000
<c.transcription>色よき花を集め。</c>
<c.translation>(I will gather fine blossoms)</c>

6
00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:32.000
<c.transcription>花の供養を取り行はゞやと存じ候。</c>
<c.translation>(and perform a memorial service for the flowers.)</c>

7
00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:25.000
<c.transcription>［ワキ］敬つて白す立花供養の事。</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] With reverence, I proclaim this memorial service for flowers.)</c>

8
00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:35.000
<c.transcription>右非情草木たりといへども。</c>
<c.translation>(Though they are said to be insentient plants,)</c>

9
00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:45.000
<c.transcription>此花広林に開けたり。</c>
<c.translation>(these flowers blossom in wide woodlands.)</c>

10
00:07:45.000 --> 00:07:59.000
<c.transcription>豈心なしといはんや。</c>
<c.translation>(How could they be said to be without feelings?)</c>

11
00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:09.000
<c.transcription>中んづく泥を出でし蓮。</c>
<c.translation>(Especially the lotus appearing from the mud)</c>

12
00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:23.000
<c.transcription>一乗妙典の題目たり。</c>
<c.translation>(and that has become the title of the one sublime law.)</c>

13
00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:32.000
<c.transcription>此結縁に引かれ。</c>
<c.translation>(Drawn by this time even plants, trees,)</c>

14
00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:52.000
<c.transcription>草木国土悉皆成仏道。</c>
<c.translation>(all the earth, achieve Buddhahood.)</c>

15
00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:17.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］手に取れば</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] As when the hand takes them,)</c>

16
00:13:17.000 --> 00:13:35.000
<c.transcription>たぶさに穢る立てながら</c>
<c.translation>(the hand itself sullies them.)</c>

17
00:13:35.000 --> 00:13:50.000
<c.transcription>三世の仏に</c>
<c.translation>(To the Buddhas of the Three Realms)</c>

18
00:13:50.000 --> 00:14:01.000
<c.transcription>花奉る。</c>
<c.translation>(I offer them as they are.)</c>

19
00:14:02.000 --> 00:14:11.000
<c.transcription>［ワキ］不思議やな今までは</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] How strange! Until now)</c>

20
00:14:11.000 --> 00:14:20.000
<c.transcription>草花りよようとして見えつる中に</c>
<c.translation>(I saw them only as flowers grasses, yet among them)</c>

21
00:14:20.000 --> 00:14:29.000
<c.transcription>白き花のおのれ独り笑の眉を</c>
<c.translation>(I see a single white flower whose brows seem)</c>

22
00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:33.000
<c.transcription>開けたるは</c>
<c.translation>(to unfold in a smile)</c>

23
00:14:33.000 --> 00:14:43.000
<c.transcription>如何なる花を立てけるぞ。</c>
<c.translation>(What manner of flower are you offering ?)</c>

24
00:14:43.000 --> 00:15:00.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］愚の御僧の仰せやな</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] A foolish question, holy priest.)</c>

25
00:15:00.000 --> 00:15:14.000
<c.transcription>黄昏時の折なるに</c>
<c.translation>(Though in this twilight hour you see it,)</c>

26
00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:34.000
<c.transcription>などかはそれと御覧ぜざる。さりながら</c>
<c.translation>(You do not recognize this flower!)</c>

27
00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:55.000
<c.transcription>名は人めきて賤しき垣ほにかゝりたれば</c>
<c.translation>(Its name seeming human, on lowly hedges it hangs,)</c>

28
00:15:55.000 --> 00:16:12.000
<c.transcription>知ろしめさぬは理なり。</c>
<c.translation>(that you do not know its name is reasonable.)</c>

29
00:16:12.000 --> 00:16:34.000
<c.transcription>是は夕顔の花にて候</c>
<c.translation>(This is the 'evening face' flower.)</c>

30
00:16:34.000 --> 00:16:46.000
<c.transcription>［ワキ］実に〳〵さぞと夕顔の</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] Indeed, it is an "evening face"!)</c>

31
00:16:46.000 --> 00:16:57.000
<c.transcription>花の主は如何なる人ぞ。</c>
<c.translation>(Who is it that has offered this flower?)</c>

32
00:16:57.000 --> 00:17:12.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］名のらずと終には知ろし召さるべし。</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] Without giving my name you will know it in the end.)</c>

33
00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:29.000
<c.transcription>我は此花の陰より参りたり。</c>
<c.translation>(I have come from this flower's shadow.)</c>

34
00:17:29.000 --> 00:17:41.000
<c.transcription>［ワキ］さては此世になき人の。</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] So then, are you no longer in the world)</c>

35
00:17:41.000 --> 00:17:52.000
<c.transcription>花の供養に逢はん為めか。</c>
<c.translation>(and came to attend this memorial service for flowers?)</c>

36
00:17:52.000 --> 00:18:04.000
<c.transcription>それに付けても名のり給へ。</c>
<c.translation>(But please, you must tell me your name.)</c>

37
00:18:04.000 --> 00:18:14.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］名は有りながら亡き跡に。</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] I have a name, though I am no longer alive,)</c>

38
00:18:14.000 --> 00:18:24.000
<c.transcription>なりし昔の物語。</c>
<c.translation>(part of an old story.)</c>

39
00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:33.000
<c.transcription>［ワキ］何某の院にも。</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] At a certain mansion,)</c>

40
00:18:33.000 --> 00:18:52.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］常はさむらふ誠には。</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] I could always be found, indeed it is so.)</c>

41
00:18:53.000 --> 00:19:15.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］五条あたりと夕顔の。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] Near Gojō, she said, of the "evening face.")</c>

42
00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:41.000
<c.transcription>五条あたりと夕顔の。</c>
<c.translation>(Near Gojō, she said, of the "evening face.")</c>

43
00:19:41.000 --> 00:19:56.000
<c.transcription>空目せし間に夢となり。</c>
<c.translation>(In the moment the eyes turn aside, she becomes a dream.)</c>

44
00:19:56.000 --> 00:20:15.000
<c.transcription>面影ばかり亡き跡の</c>
<c.translation>(Only her image lingers behind)</c>

45
00:20:15.000 --> 00:20:34.000
<c.transcription>立花の陰に隠れけり。</c>
<c.translation>(as she disapperas in the shadow of the flowers.)</c>

46
00:20:34.000 --> 00:21:02.000
<c.transcription>立花の陰に隠れけり。</c>
<c.translation>(She disappears in the shadow of the flowers.)</c>

47
00:23:17.000 --> 00:23:23.000
<c.transcription>（狂言）かように候う者は、</c>
<c.translation>([KYŌGEN] I am someone who lives)</c>

48
00:23:23.000 --> 00:23:35.000
<c.transcription>都北山あたりに、住まいする者にて候、</c>
<c.translation>(in the Kitayama area of the capital.)</c>

49
00:23:35.000 --> 00:23:40.000
<c.transcription>承り候えば、</c>
<c.translation>(I have heard that near here,)</c>

50
00:23:40.000 --> 00:23:52.000
<c.transcription>あたり近き、雲林院において、一夏の間、</c>
<c.translation>(at Unrin-in, there will be memorial services)</c>

51
00:23:52.000 --> 00:24:00.000
<c.transcription>花の供養の御座候よし、</c>
<c.translation>(for the lowers offered over the summer.)</c>

52
00:24:00.000 --> 00:24:18.000
<c.transcription>承りおよびて候ほどに我らも、参らばやと存ずる、</c>
<c.translation>(This being the case, I too, intend to go there.)</c>

53
00:24:18.000 --> 00:24:29.000
<c.transcription>まことに、今日った参る人も少なく、</c>
<c.translation>(Truly, as few people are going there this evening,)</c>

54
00:24:29.000 --> 00:24:37.000
<c.transcription>何とやらん、ものさびて候よ、</c>
<c.translation>(it is rather melancholy.)</c>

55
00:24:37.000 --> 00:24:53.000
<c.transcription>（ワキ）のうのう方々はこの辺りの人にて候か、</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI ]Ho, there! Are you someone from around here ?)</c>

56
00:24:53.000 --> 00:25:00.000
<c.transcription>（狂言）なかなかこの辺りの者にて候、</c>
<c.translation>([KYŌGEN]  Indeed, I am a person from this area.)</c>

57
00:25:00.000 --> 00:25:13.000
<c.transcription>（ワキ）左様に候わば、まず近こう御入り候え、ものを</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] If that's the case, first of all, could you come closer ?)</c>

58
00:25:13.000 --> 00:25:18.000
<c.transcription>尋ねたきことの候、</c>
<c.translation>(There is something I would like to ask you.)</c>

59
00:25:18.000 --> 00:25:24.000
<c.transcription>（狂言）心得申して候</c>
<c.translation>([KYŌGEN] Certainly.)</c>

60
00:25:38.000 --> 00:25:45.000
<c.transcription>さて、御尋ねなされたきとは、</c>
<c.translation>(Well then, what is the matter)</c>

61
00:25:45.000 --> 00:25:53.000
<c.transcription>如何様なる、御用にて候ぞ、</c>
<c.translation>(you would like to ask me about ?)</c>

62
00:25:53.000 --> 00:26:04.000
<c.transcription>（ワキ）思し召しよらざる申し事にて候えども</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] While it isn't a circumstance of much importance,)</c>

63
00:26:04.000 --> 00:26:18.000
<c.transcription>古しえ、五条辺りに、夕顔の上の住ませ給いし仔細、</c>
<c.translation>(I would like you to tell me the particulars of the story of Lady Yūgao,)</c>

64
00:26:18.000 --> 00:26:24.000
<c.transcription>御物語候え、</c>
<c.translation>(of the Evening Faces, who lived here long ago.)</c>

65
00:26:24.000 --> 00:26:37.000
<c.transcription>（狂言）これは思いも寄らぬ事を、御尋ねなされ候ものかな、</c>
<c.translation>([KYŌGEN] This is an unexpected request you've made of me.)</c>

66
00:26:37.000 --> 00:26:51.000
<c.transcription>我等も左様の事詳しくは存ぜず候が、およそ、</c>
<c.translation>(I don't know about the situation in much detail, but)</c>

67
00:26:51.000 --> 00:27:03.000
<c.transcription>承りたる通り、物語申そうずるにて候、</c>
<c.translation>(I will do the best I can to tell you the story as I have heard it.)</c>

68
00:27:11.000 --> 00:27:25.000
<c.transcription>さる程に、夕顔の上と申したる、御方は、</c>
<c.translation>(Well then, the one known as Lady Yūgao was the daughter)</c>

69
00:27:25.000 --> 00:27:34.000
<c.transcription>三位の中将の、御息女にて、</c>
<c.translation>(of a middle captain of the third rank, and,)</c>

70
00:27:34.000 --> 00:27:40.000
<c.transcription>さる仔細の事候いて、</c>
<c.translation>(owing the certain circumstances,)</c>

71
00:27:40.000 --> 00:27:53.000
<c.transcription>五条辺りに忍び居て御座ありたると申す、</c>
<c.translation>(she came to live in seclusion in the area of Gojo.)</c>

72
00:27:53.000 --> 00:28:01.000
<c.transcription>またその頃、光源氏は、</c>
<c.translation>(Also at the at time, Hikaru Genji)</c>

73
00:28:01.000 --> 00:28:14.000
<c.transcription>六条御息所の方へ御通いなされ候が、</c>
<c.translation>(was paying regular visit to the home of Lady Rokujo.)</c>

74
00:28:14.000 --> 00:28:24.000
<c.transcription>折節五条辺りを、通られしかば、</c>
<c.translation>(On occasion he would pass through the Gojo area)</c>

75
00:28:24.000 --> 00:28:31.000
<c.transcription>しょうやに夕顔の花、</c>
<c.translation>(and it happened that there was a simple dwelling there)</c>

76
00:28:31.000 --> 00:28:40.000
<c.transcription>見事に咲き乱れ候程に、</c>
<c.translation>(with "evening faces" blooming in splendid profusion.)</c>

77
00:28:40.000 --> 00:28:46.000
<c.transcription>惟光をめされ、あの花、</c>
<c.translation>(He called Koremitsu to him,)</c>

78
00:28:46.000 --> 00:28:54.000
<c.transcription>手折りてまいれとの御事なり、</c>
<c.translation>(and requested that he go pluck a blossom.)</c>

79
00:28:54.000 --> 00:29:10.000
<c.transcription>惟光御随身をもって、その花を所望申されしかば、</c>
<c.translation>(When Koremitsu spoke to his attendant,)</c>

80
00:29:10.000 --> 00:29:16.000
<c.transcription>しょうやより童を出だし、</c>
<c.translation>(a child came out of the house, and,)</c>

81
00:29:16.000 --> 00:29:25.000
<c.transcription>しばらくそれに、御待ちあれとて、</c>
<c.translation>(having asked that he wait there for a wile, soon after,)</c>

82
00:29:25.000 --> 00:29:37.000
<c.transcription>その後、白き扇の、つまいと焦がしたるに、</c>
<c.translation>(offered him a white fan, its edges perfumed with incense,)</c>

83
00:29:37.000 --> 00:29:46.000
<c.transcription>夕顔の花をそえて指し出だす、</c>
<c.translation>(on which rested a blossom of the "evening faces".)</c>

84
00:29:46.000 --> 00:29:58.000
<c.transcription>御随身これを受け取り、惟光に参らせければ、</c>
<c.translation>(The attendant took this and returned with it to Koremitsu.)</c>

85
00:29:58.000 --> 00:30:08.000
<c.transcription>惟光、源氏へ参らせ候ところに、</c>
<c.translation>(Koremistu went with it to Genji, who,)</c>

86
00:30:08.000 --> 00:30:21.000
<c.transcription>その扇の縁に、一首の歌の御座候ほどに、</c>
<c.translation>(seeing then that there was a poem on the edge of the fan,)</c>

87
00:30:21.000 --> 00:30:27.000
<c.transcription>急ぎ御返歌をなされ、</c>
<c.translation>(quickly wrote a verse in reply.)</c>

88
00:30:27.000 --> 00:30:38.000
<c.transcription>その花ゆえに、夕顔の上に見え給い、</c>
<c.translation>(Because of that flower, he was drawn to the Lady Yūgao,)</c>

89
00:30:38.000 --> 00:30:46.000
<c.transcription>御契り浅からねば、その後、</c>
<c.translation>(of the evening faces, and as the vows they shared were not shallow,)</c>

90
00:30:46.000 --> 00:30:55.000
<c.transcription>何某院へ御伴いなされ、</c>
<c.translation>(after that he came to stay together with her there at her dwelling.)</c>

91
00:30:55.000 --> 00:31:03.000
<c.transcription>色々比翼連理の契り</c>
<c.translation>(Even as the purity of the many pledges)</c>

92
00:31:03.000 --> 00:31:09.000
<c.transcription>浅からず候ところに、</c>
<c.translation>(they exchanged were profound-)</c>

93
00:31:09.000 --> 00:31:18.000
<c.transcription>なんぼう、不思議なる事にて候、</c>
<c.translation>(By the Sacred Treaures! Mysteroiusly,)</c>

94
00:31:18.000 --> 00:31:29.000
<c.transcription>夕顔の上は、物怪に犯され給ひ、</c>
<c.translation>(Lady Yūgao was possessed)</c>

95
00:31:29.000 --> 00:31:37.000
<c.transcription>空しくなられたると申す、</c>
<c.translation>(by some sort of vengeful spirit, and it is said that all was lost...)</c>

96
00:31:37.000 --> 00:31:46.000
<c.transcription>光源氏の御嘆き申すも、</c>
<c.translation>(As to Hikaru Genji's grief, its depth was limitless)</c>

97
00:31:46.000 --> 00:31:59.000
<c.transcription>愚かなる体にて御座ありたると申す、</c>
<c.translation>(as there was nothing to be done for her, it is said.)</c>

98
00:31:59.000 --> 00:32:07.000
<c.transcription>まず、我らの承りたる仔細、</c>
<c.translation>(In any event, those are the details,)</c>

99
00:32:07.000 --> 00:32:16.000
<c.transcription>大方かくのごとくにて候が、</c>
<c.translation>(at least in broad terms, as I know them.)</c>

100
00:32:16.000 --> 00:32:24.000
<c.transcription>只今はなにと、思し召してやらん、</c>
<c.translation>(But why are you interested in this)</c>

101
00:32:24.000 --> 00:32:33.000
<c.transcription>御尋ね不審に存じ候、</c>
<c.translation>(and asking me about this matter now ? I find it suspicious.)</c>

102
00:32:33.000 --> 00:32:43.000
<c.transcription>（ワキ）懇ろに承り候ものかな、</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] I'm grateful that you have described the matter so thoroughly.)</c>

103
00:32:43.000 --> 00:32:52.000
<c.transcription>それがし一夏の間、花の供養を</c>
<c.translation>(When I was performing a memorial service for flowers)</c>

104
00:32:52.000 --> 00:32:58.000
<c.transcription>執り行い候ところに、</c>
<c.translation>(offered during the summer, a woman appeared)</c>

105
00:32:58.000 --> 00:33:11.000
<c.transcription>女性一人白き花をたてられ候ほどに、</c>
<c.translation>(and gave me a white flower.)</c>

106
00:33:11.000 --> 00:33:17.000
<c.transcription>花の主はいかなる人ぞと</c>
<c.translation>(I asked who, and what sort of person, she was with the flower,)</c>

107
00:33:17.000 --> 00:33:25.000
<c.transcription>尋ねて候えば、それにつき</c>
<c.translation>(to which she replied speaking of the Lady of the Evening Faces)</c>

108
00:33:25.000 --> 00:33:38.000
<c.transcription>夕顔の上の御事を我が身の上の様に言い捨て、</c>
<c.translation>(as though she spoke of herself.)</c>

109
00:33:38.000 --> 00:33:46.000
<c.transcription>そのまま花の陰にて姿を</c>
<c.translation>(Then she disappeared in the shadow of the flowers.)</c>

110
00:33:46.000 --> 00:33:51.000
<c.transcription>見失いて候よ</c>
<c.translation>(That's what happened.)</c>

111
00:33:51.000 --> 00:34:01.000
<c.transcription>（狂言）言語道断、不思議なる事を</c>
<c.translation>([KYŌGEN] How astonishing!)</c>

112
00:34:01.000 --> 00:34:06.000
<c.transcription>仰せ候ものかな、</c>
<c.translation>(What a wondrous thing you have related to me.)</c>

113
00:34:06.000 --> 00:34:12.000
<c.transcription>さては我らが推量申すに、</c>
<c.translation>(Now then, if I may say what I suppose, it can only be that)</c>

114
00:34:12.000 --> 00:34:23.000
<c.transcription>斯様に花の供養の御座候間、</c>
<c.translation>(when you were performing the memorial service for flowers,)</c>

115
00:34:23.000 --> 00:34:37.000
<c.transcription>夕顔の花の精、または古え夕顔の上ご亡心、</c>
<c.translation>(the spirit of the "yugao flower", and also the ghost of Lady Yūgao,)</c>

116
00:34:37.000 --> 00:34:48.000
<c.transcription>現れ出たると存じ候がしかとは存ぜず候、</c>
<c.translation>(Lady of the Evening Faces, of long ago appeared before you.)</c>

117
00:34:48.000 --> 00:34:59.000
<c.transcription>去りながら、お僧尊くましますにより</c>
<c.translation>(This being the case, I believe that due to)</c>

118
00:34:59.000 --> 00:35:06.000
<c.transcription>御弔いにも預かりたく思し召し、</c>
<c.translation>(the merit emanating from your Reverence,)</c>

119
00:35:06.000 --> 00:35:12.000
<c.transcription>夕顔の上のご亡心</c>
<c.translation>(the spirit of the Lady Yūgao appeared to you in order)</c>

120
00:35:12.000 --> 00:35:20.000
<c.transcription>現れ出たると存じ候、</c>
<c.translation>(to ask that you offer prayers for her deliverance.)</c>

121
00:35:20.000 --> 00:35:35.000
<c.transcription>左様に候はばこれより五条辺りへ御出で候はば、</c>
<c.translation>(If that is the case, you should go now to the Gojo area,)</c>

122
00:35:35.000 --> 00:35:43.000
<c.transcription>奇特なることも御座候ほどに、</c>
<c.translation>(where a miracle will surely occur. Then you should pray earnestly)</c>

123
00:35:43.000 --> 00:35:57.000
<c.transcription>そののち懇ろに弔うて御通りあれかしと存じ候、</c>
<c.translation>(for her enlightenment as she has requested of you.)</c>

124
00:35:57.000 --> 00:36:06.000
<c.transcription>（ワキ）我らも左様に存じ候間、</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] As I also believe this to be true,)</c>

125
00:36:06.000 --> 00:36:13.000
<c.transcription>五条辺りに立ち出で、</c>
<c.translation>(I will go to the Gojo area and pray there)</c>

126
00:36:13.000 --> 00:36:25.000
<c.transcription>夕顔の上の御跡を弔い申そうずるにて候、</c>
<c.translation>(For the ghost of the Lady Yūgao and her deliverance.)</c>

127
00:36:25.000 --> 00:36:38.000
<c.transcription>（狂言）それは近頃にて候、お僧御出にて候はば</c>
<c.translation>([KYŌGEN] As you will be going there shortly,)</c>

128
00:36:38.000 --> 00:36:49.000
<c.transcription>我らも御後より参ろうずるにて候、</c>
<c.translation>(I'll follow after your Recerence in a while.)</c>

129
00:36:49.000 --> 00:36:56.000
<c.transcription>（ワキ）やがて後より来られ候え、</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] In due time then, I will expect you there.)</c>

130
00:36:56.000 --> 00:37:02.000
<c.transcription>（狂言）心得申して候、</c>
<c.translation>([KYŌGEN] I'll do as you say.)</c>

131
00:39:23.000 --> 00:39:32.000
<c.transcription>［ワキ］有りし教へに随つて</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] Following what I was told earlier)</c>

132
00:39:32.000 --> 00:39:43.000
<c.transcription>五条あたりに来て見れば</c>
<c.translation>(I have to go to Gojo to see:)</c>

133
00:39:43.000 --> 00:39:55.000
<c.transcription>実にも昔の居まし所</c>
<c.translation>(Indeed, the mansion, as in the past,)</c>

134
00:39:55.000 --> 00:40:09.000
<c.transcription>さながら宿りも夕顔の</c>
<c.translation>(the dwelling and its evening faces.)</c>

135
00:40:09.000 --> 00:40:18.000
<c.transcription>瓢簞しば〳〵空し</c>
<c.translation>(Gourds now often empty,)</c>

136
00:40:18.000 --> 00:40:43.000
<c.transcription>草顔淵が巷に滋し。</c>
<c.translation>(and (Genken's) Yen Yūan's home overgrown with weeds.)</c>

137
00:42:15.000 --> 00:42:49.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］藜藋深く鎖せり。</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] Densely closed off by goosefoot,)</c>

138
00:42:49.000 --> 00:43:10.000
<c.transcription>夕陽の残晴新に</c>
<c.translation>(the evening sun creates mountain shadows,)</c>

139
00:43:10.000 --> 00:43:35.000
<c.transcription>窓を穿つて去る。</c>
<c.translation>(comes through the window and then leaves.)</c>

140
00:43:35.000 --> 00:43:57.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］愁嘆の泉の声。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] The faint sound of a hidden spring.)</c>

141
00:43:57.000 --> 00:44:42.000
<c.transcription>雨原憲が枢を湿ほす。</c>
<c.translation>(Rain dampens Genken's (Yüan Hsien) gate.)</c>

142
00:44:43.000 --> 00:44:58.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］さらでも袖を湿ほすは</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] But what dampens the sleeves is)</c>

143
00:44:58.000 --> 00:45:27.000
<c.transcription>廬山の雪の曙。</c>
<c.translation>(dawn on the snow on Mount Lu.)</c>

144
00:45:40.000 --> 00:46:04.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］窓頭に向ふ朗月は。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] Through the east window the limpid moon,)</c>

145
00:46:15.000 --> 00:46:34.000
<c.transcription>窓頭に向ふ朗月は。</c>
<c.translation>(Through the east window the limpid moon,)</c>

146
00:46:34.000 --> 00:46:47.000
<c.transcription>琴瑟に当り</c>
<c.translation>(on the zither stand casts its light.)</c>

147
00:46:47.000 --> 00:47:03.000
<c.transcription>愁傷の秋の山。</c>
<c.translation>(Beyond the hedge, the autumn mountains.)</c>

148
00:47:03.000 --> 00:47:14.000
<c.transcription>物すごの気色や。</c>
<c.translation>(Such a desolate evening!)</c>

149
00:47:15.000 --> 00:47:27.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］実に物すごき風の音。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] Indeed, the desolate sound of the wind,)</c>

150
00:47:27.000 --> 00:47:38.000
<c.transcription>簀戸の竹垣有りし世の。</c>
<c.translation>(the wicker bamboo fence as in the past.)</c>

151
00:47:38.000 --> 00:47:50.000
<c.transcription>夢の姿を見せ給へ。</c>
<c.translation>(Please show me your form in a dream)</c>

152
00:47:50.000 --> 00:48:07.000
<c.transcription>菩提を深く弔らはん。</c>
<c.translation>(I will pray in earnest for your soul.)</c>

153
00:48:07.000 --> 00:48:30.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］山の端の。心も知らで行く月は</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] The moon, uncertain of the mountain ridge as it went)</c>

154
00:48:30.000 --> 00:48:48.000
<c.transcription>上の空にて絶えし跡の。</c>
<c.translation>(and disappeared in the sky high above without a trace.)</c>

155
00:48:48.000 --> 00:49:03.000
<c.transcription>又いつか逢ふべき。</c>
<c.translation>(When will they meet again ?)</c>

156
00:49:03.000 --> 00:49:23.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］山賤の。垣ほ荒るとき折々は</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] Though the mountain dweller's fence has fallen into ruin, from time to time)</c>

157
00:49:23.000 --> 00:49:38.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］哀をかけよ撫子の。</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] Show compassion for the wild pink)</c>

158
00:49:38.000 --> 00:49:51.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］花の姿をまみえなば。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] Blossom, if I reaveal the form)</c>

159
00:49:51.000 --> 00:49:59.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］跡訪ふべきか。</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] Will you pray for my soul ?)</c>

160
00:49:59.000 --> 00:50:06.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］中々に。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] Certainly, I will.)</c>

161
00:50:06.000 --> 00:50:33.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］さらばと思ひ夕顔の。</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] Thinking, "well then,"  the "evening face")</c>

162
00:50:33.000 --> 00:50:58.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］草の半蔀おし上げて。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] The vine-covered lattice shutter pushes open,)</c>

163
00:50:58.000 --> 00:51:13.000
<c.transcription>立ち出づる御姿。</c>
<c.translation>(revealing her form as she steps out.)</c>

164
00:51:13.000 --> 00:51:43.000
<c.transcription>見るに涙のとゞまらず。</c>
<c.translation>(At the sight tears flow without stopping.)</c>

165
00:52:04.000 --> 00:52:19.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］其頃源氏の。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] At that time, Genji)</c>

166
00:52:19.000 --> 00:52:31.000
<c.transcription>中将と聞こえしは</c>
<c.translation>(the Middle Captain as he was called,)</c>

167
00:52:31.000 --> 00:52:45.000
<c.transcription>此夕顔の草枕。</c>
<c.translation>(shared the grass pillow of this "evenig face" for a brief rest.)</c>

168
00:52:45.000 --> 00:53:03.000
<c.transcription>たゞ仮臥の夜もすがら</c>
<c.translation>(Through the night they heard from next door)</c>

169
00:53:03.000 --> 00:53:18.000
<c.transcription>隣を聞けば三吉野や。</c>
<c.translation>(a pilgrim's voice in prayer)</c>

170
00:53:18.000 --> 00:53:39.000
<c.transcription>御嶽精進の御声にて。</c>
<c.translation>(about ascending the sacred peak at Miyoshino.)</c>

171
00:53:39.000 --> 00:54:30.000
<c.transcription>南無当来導師。弥勒仏とぞ称へける。</c>
<c.translation>("Save us, holy guide of the way in the future, Maitreya Buddha!", he chanted.)</c>

172
00:54:30.000 --> 00:54:59.000
<c.transcription>今も尊き御供養に。其時の思ひ</c>
<c.translation>(Even now this service has brought back the memory)</c>

173
00:54:59.000 --> 00:55:33.000
<c.transcription>出でられて。そゞろに濡るゝ袂かな。</c>
<c.translation>(of that time and unmittingly tears dampen my sleeves.)</c>

174
00:55:46.000 --> 00:56:05.000
<c.transcription>猶それよりも忘れぬは</c>
<c.translation>(But more than that, I cannot forget the evening)</c>

175
00:56:05.000 --> 00:56:30.000
<c.transcription>源氏此宿を。見そめ給ひし夕つ方。</c>
<c.translation>(when Genji first saw this house.)</c>

176
00:56:30.000 --> 00:56:40.000
<c.transcription>惟光を招き寄せ。</c>
<c.translation>(Beckoning to Koremitsu,)</c>

177
00:56:40.000 --> 00:57:00.000
<c.transcription>あの花折れと宣へば。</c>
<c.translation>("Pick that flower for me," he ordered.)</c>

178
00:57:00.000 --> 00:57:22.000
<c.transcription>白き扇の。つまいたう焦がしたりしに。</c>
<c.translation>(On a white fan, its edges perfumed with incense,)</c>

179
00:57:22.000 --> 00:57:46.000
<c.transcription>此花を折りて参らする。</c>
<c.translation>(the flower was picked and presented.)</c>

180
00:57:46.000 --> 00:58:10.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］源氏つくづくと御覧じて。</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] Genji, gazing at it intently,)</c>

181
00:58:10.000 --> 00:58:32.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］打ち渡す 遠方人に問ふとても。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] "Of you passing in the distance..." he asked)</c>

182
00:58:32.000 --> 00:58:52.000
<c.transcription>それ其花と答へずは。</c>
<c.translation>(and if I had not answered about the flower)</c>

183
00:58:52.000 --> 00:59:30.000
<c.transcription>終に知らでもあるべきに。逢ひに扇を手に触るゝ。</c>
<c.translation>(forever we must have remained strangers. We were brought together)</c>

184
00:59:30.000 --> 00:59:49.000
<c.transcription>契の程のうれしさ。</c>
<c.translation>(by the fan touched by our hands, in a joyous pledge of love.)</c>

185
00:59:49.000 --> 01:00:05.000
<c.transcription>折々尋ね寄るならば。</c>
<c.translation>(If from time to time)</c>

186
01:00:05.000 --> 01:00:19.000
<c.transcription>定めぬ海士の此宿の。</c>
<c.translation>(I visit this dwelling of a homeless fishergirl)</c>

187
01:00:19.000 --> 01:00:42.000
<c.transcription>主を誰と白波の。</c>
<c.translation>(not knowing the owner's name, I hope)</c>

188
01:00:42.000 --> 01:01:01.000
<c.transcription>よるべの末を頼まんと</c>
<c.translation>(to be as white foam finding at last the shore, he thought,)</c>

189
01:01:01.000 --> 01:01:30.000
<c.transcription>一首を詠じおはします。</c>
<c.translation>(and composed a poem.)</c>

190
01:01:36.000 --> 01:02:24.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］折りてこそ。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] If you pick it)</c>

191
01:17:26.000 --> 01:17:40.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］折りてこそ</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] If you pick it)</c>

192
01:17:40.000 --> 01:17:52.000
<c.transcription>それかとも見め</c>
<c.translation>(then, indeed you will know it)</c>

193
01:17:52.000 --> 01:18:15.000
<c.transcription>黄昏に。</c>
<c.translation>(in the twilight)</c>

194
01:18:19.000 --> 01:18:36.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］ほのぼの見えし</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] Faintly visible:)</c>

195
01:18:36.000 --> 01:18:48.000
<c.transcription>花の夕顔。</c>
<c.translation>(The flowering "evening face",)</c>

196
01:18:48.000 --> 01:19:00.000
<c.transcription>花の夕顔。</c>
<c.translation>(the flowering "evening face",)</c>

197
01:19:00.000 --> 01:19:29.000
<c.transcription>花の夕顔。</c>
<c.translation>(the flowering "evening face".)</c>

198
01:19:29.000 --> 01:19:57.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］終の宿りは知らせ申しつ。</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] "As my final home I have shown you)</c>

199
01:19:57.000 --> 01:20:14.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］常にはとむらひ。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] Always pray for me)</c>

200
01:20:14.000 --> 01:20:28.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］おはしませと。</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] I beg you", she said, and)</c>

201
01:20:28.000 --> 01:20:44.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］木綿附の鳥の音。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] as she spoke the crowing of the cocks,)</c>

202
01:20:44.000 --> 01:21:00.000
<c.transcription>［シテ］鐘もしきりに。</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] The tolling of the bells too,)</c>

203
01:21:00.000 --> 01:21:14.000
<c.transcription>告げ渡る東雲。</c>
<c.translation>(announce the coming of dawn.)</c>

204
01:21:14.000 --> 01:21:29.000
<c.transcription>［地謡］あさまにもなりぬべし。</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] As nothing will be hidden in the morning light,)</c>

205
01:21:29.000 --> 01:21:56.000
<c.transcription>明けぬ先にと夕顔の宿り。</c>
<c.translation>("Before dawn breaks, to the dwelling of the "evening face",)</c>

206
01:21:56.000 --> 01:22:24.000
<c.transcription>明けぬ先にと夕顔の宿りの。</c>
<c.translation>("before dawn breaks, to the dwelling of the "evening face",)</c>

207
01:22:24.000 --> 01:22:57.000
<c.transcription>又半蔀の内に入りて</c>
<c.translation>(she says, and again goes within the lattice shutter,)</c>

208
01:22:57.000 --> 01:23:49.000
<c.transcription>其まま夢とぞなりにける。</c>
<c.translation>(just so, becoming one with the dream.)</c>